{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":342,"text":"For a long time in my life,"},{"time":3101,"text":"I felt like I'd been living two different lives."},{"time":7692,"text":"There's the life that everyone sees,"},{"time":11097,"text":"and then there's the life that only I see."},{"time":14804,"text":"And in the life that everyone sees,"},{"time":17324,"text":"who I am is a friend,"},{"time":19798,"text":"a son, a brother,"},{"time":22353,"text":"a stand-up comedian and a teenager."},{"time":25979,"text":"That's the life everyone sees."},{"time":27820,"text":"If you were to ask my friends and family to describe me,"},{"time":29346,"text":"that's what they would tell you."},{"time":31185,"text":"And that's a huge part of me. That is who I am."},{"time":33183,"text":"And if you were to ask me to describe myself,"},{"time":35993,"text":"I'd probably say some of those same things."},{"time":38915,"text":"And I wouldn't be lying,"},{"time":42476,"text":"but I wouldn't totally be telling you the truth, either,"},{"time":46006,"text":"because the truth is,"},{"time":47533,"text":"that's just the life everyone else sees."},{"time":50705,"text":"In the life that only I see, who I am,"},{"time":54468,"text":"who I really am,"},{"time":56395,"text":"is someone who struggles intensely with depression."},{"time":60830,"text":"I have for the last six years of my life,"},{"time":63507,"text":"and I continue to every day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68626,"text":"Now, for someone who has never experienced depression"},{"time":71123,"text":"or doesn't really know what that means,"},{"time":72325,"text":"that might surprise them to hear,"},{"time":73708,"text":"because there's this pretty popular misconception"},{"time":75613,"text":"that depression is just being sad"},{"time":78360,"text":"when something in your life goes wrong,"},{"time":80848,"text":"when you break up with your girlfriend,"},{"time":82490,"text":"when you lose a loved one,"},{"time":83881,"text":"when you don't get the job you wanted."},{"time":85632,"text":"But that's sadness. That's a natural thing."},{"time":87619,"text":"That's a natural human emotion."},{"time":89531,"text":"Real depression isn't being sad"},{"time":93729,"text":"when something in your life goes wrong."},{"time":96358,"text":"Real depression is being sad"},{"time":98144,"text":"when everything in your life is going right."},{"time":101413,"text":"That's real depression, and that's what I suffer from."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103898,"text":"And to be totally honest,"},{"time":106023,"text":"that's hard for me to stand up here and say."},{"time":108837,"text":"It's hard for me to talk about,"},{"time":110558,"text":"and it seems to be hard for everyone to talk about,"},{"time":113321,"text":"so much so that no one's talking about it."},{"time":115689,"text":"And no one's talking about depression, but we need to be,"},{"time":118083,"text":"because right now it's a massive problem."},{"time":121825,"text":"It's a massive problem."},{"time":123495,"text":"But we don't see it on social media, right?"},{"time":125297,"text":"We don't see it on Facebook. We don't see it on Twitter."},{"time":127385,"text":"We don't see it on the news, because it's not happy,"},{"time":129207,"text":"it's not fun, it's not light."},{"time":130836,"text":"And so because we don't see it, we don't see the severity of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134431,"text":"But the severity of it and the seriousness of it is this:"},{"time":138190,"text":"every 30 seconds,"},{"time":139913,"text":"every 30 seconds, somewhere,"},{"time":142117,"text":"someone in the world takes their own life"},{"time":144310,"text":"because of depression,"},{"time":145387,"text":"and it might be two blocks away, it might be two countries away,"},{"time":147627,"text":"it might be two continents away, but it's happening,"},{"time":149157,"text":"and it's happening every single day."},{"time":151727,"text":"And we have a tendency, as a society,"},{"time":154691,"text":"to look at that and go, \"So what?\""},{"time":159937,"text":"So what? We look at that, and we go, \"That's your problem."},{"time":164592,"text":"That's their problem.\""},{"time":166995,"text":"We say we're sad and we say we're sorry,"},{"time":168847,"text":"but we also say, \"So what?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":170224,"text":"Well, two years ago it was my problem,"},{"time":174907,"text":"because I sat on the edge of my bed"},{"time":178964,"text":"where I'd sat a million times before"},{"time":182324,"text":"and I was suicidal."},{"time":185140,"text":"I was suicidal, and if you were to look at my life on the surface,"},{"time":189066,"text":"you wouldn't see a kid who was suicidal."},{"time":191308,"text":"You'd see a kid who was the captain of his basketball team,"},{"time":193424,"text":"the drama and theater student of the year,"},{"time":195485,"text":"the English student of the year,"},{"time":196444,"text":"someone who was consistently on the honor roll"},{"time":198272,"text":"and consistently at every party."},{"time":201945,"text":"So you would say I wasn't depressed, you would say"},{"time":203586,"text":"I wasn't suicidal, but you would be wrong."},{"time":206297,"text":"You would be wrong. So I sat there that night"},{"time":207736,"text":"beside a bottle of pills with a pen and paper in my hand"},{"time":211774,"text":"and I thought about taking my own life"},{"time":213762,"text":"and I came this close to doing it."},{"time":217114,"text":"I came this close to doing it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218796,"text":"And I didn't, so that makes me one of the lucky ones,"},{"time":221924,"text":"one of the people who gets to step out on the ledge"},{"time":224059,"text":"and look down but not jump,"},{"time":226320,"text":"one of the lucky ones who survives."},{"time":228325,"text":"Well, I survived, and that just leaves me with my story,"},{"time":230722,"text":"and my story is this:"},{"time":233127,"text":"In four simple words, I suffer from depression."},{"time":236480,"text":"I suffer from depression,"},{"time":238910,"text":"and for a long time, I think,"},{"time":246230,"text":"I was living two totally different lives,"},{"time":248826,"text":"where one person was always afraid of the other."},{"time":250687,"text":"I was afraid that people would see me for who I really was,"},{"time":252786,"text":"that I wasn't the perfect, popular kid in high school everyone thought I was,"},{"time":256028,"text":"that beneath my smile, there was struggle,"},{"time":258453,"text":"and beneath my light, there was dark,"},{"time":260416,"text":"and beneath my big personality just hid even bigger pain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264793,"text":"See, some people might fear girls not liking them back."},{"time":267430,"text":"Some people might fear sharks. Some people might fear death."},{"time":269519,"text":"But for me, for a large part of my life, I feared myself."},{"time":274212,"text":"I feared my truth, I feared my honesty, I feared my vulnerability,"},{"time":276904,"text":"and that fear made me feel"},{"time":279126,"text":"like I was forced into a corner,"},{"time":281483,"text":"like I was forced into a corner and there was only one way out,"},{"time":284513,"text":"and so I thought about that way every single day."},{"time":288306,"text":"I thought about it every single day,"},{"time":289753,"text":"and if I'm being totally honest, standing here"},{"time":291424,"text":"I've thought about it again since, because that's the sickness,"},{"time":294797,"text":"that's the struggle, that's depression,"},{"time":296731,"text":"and depression isn't chicken pox."},{"time":297950,"text":"You don't beat it once and it's gone forever."},{"time":299668,"text":"It's something you live with. It's something you live in."},{"time":302431,"text":"It's the roommate you can't kick out. It's the voice you can't ignore."},{"time":306003,"text":"It's the feelings you can't seem to escape,"},{"time":308264,"text":"the scariest part is that after a while,"},{"time":313337,"text":"you become numb to it. It becomes normal for you,"},{"time":316217,"text":"and what you really fear the most"},{"time":318504,"text":"isn't the suffering inside of you."},{"time":321360,"text":"It's the stigma inside of others,"},{"time":322876,"text":"it's the shame, it's the embarrassment,"},{"time":325157,"text":"it's the disapproving look on a friend's face,"},{"time":327610,"text":"it's the whispers in the hallway that you're weak,"},{"time":331074,"text":"it's the comments that you're crazy."},{"time":332475,"text":"That's what keeps you from getting help."},{"time":334575,"text":"That's what makes you hold it in and hide it."},{"time":337569,"text":"It's the stigma. So you hold it in and you hide it,"},{"time":339904,"text":"and you hold it in and you hide it,"},{"time":341766,"text":"and even though it's keeping you in bed every day"},{"time":343442,"text":"and it's making your life feel empty no matter how much you try and fill it,"},{"time":346382,"text":"you hide it, because the stigma in our society"},{"time":348545,"text":"around depression is very real."},{"time":351460,"text":"It's very real, and if you think that it isn't, ask yourself this:"},{"time":354662,"text":"Would you rather make your next Facebook status"},{"time":356471,"text":"say you're having a tough time getting out of bed"},{"time":358217,"text":"because you hurt your back"},{"time":360366,"text":"or you're having a tough time getting out of bed every morning"},{"time":362358,"text":"because you're depressed?"},{"time":364458,"text":"That's the stigma, because unfortunately,"},{"time":366742,"text":"we live in a world where if you break your arm,"},{"time":369210,"text":"everyone runs over to sign your cast,"},{"time":371899,"text":"but if you tell people you're depressed, everyone runs the other way."},{"time":374700,"text":"That's the stigma."},{"time":377200,"text":"We are so, so, so accepting of any body part breaking down"},{"time":382166,"text":"other than our brains. And that's ignorance."},{"time":385268,"text":"That's pure ignorance, and that ignorance has created"},{"time":387280,"text":"a world that doesn't understand depression,"},{"time":388844,"text":"that doesn't understand mental health."},{"time":391350,"text":"And that's ironic to me, because depression"},{"time":393303,"text":"is one of the best documented problems we have in the world,"},{"time":395813,"text":"yet it's one of the least discussed."},{"time":397858,"text":"We just push it aside and put it in a corner"},{"time":400294,"text":"and pretend it's not there and hope it'll fix itself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403881,"text":"Well, it won't. It hasn't, and it's not going to,"},{"time":407223,"text":"because that's wishful thinking,"},{"time":409114,"text":"and wishful thinking isn't a game plan, it's procrastination,"},{"time":411887,"text":"and we can't procrastinate on something this important."},{"time":416816,"text":"The first step in solving any problem"},{"time":420207,"text":"is recognizing there is one."},{"time":421690,"text":"Well, we haven't done that, so we can't really expect"},{"time":424448,"text":"to find an answer when we're still afraid of the question."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427633,"text":"And I don't know what the solution is."},{"time":431412,"text":"I wish I did, but I don't -- but I think,"},{"time":433873,"text":"I think it has to start here."},{"time":435881,"text":"It has to start with me, it has to start with you,"},{"time":438280,"text":"it has to start with the people who are suffering,"},{"time":441698,"text":"the ones who are hidden in the shadows."},{"time":443115,"text":"We need to speak up and shatter the silence."},{"time":445115,"text":"We need to be the ones who are brave for what we believe in,"},{"time":447434,"text":"because if there's one thing that I've come to realize,"},{"time":450609,"text":"if there's one thing that I see as the biggest problem,"},{"time":454185,"text":"it's not in building a world"},{"time":457224,"text":"where we eliminate the ignorance of others."},{"time":460973,"text":"It's in building a world where we teach the acceptance of ourselves,"},{"time":464259,"text":"where we're okay with who we are,"},{"time":465460,"text":"because when we get honest,"},{"time":466960,"text":"we see that we all struggle and we all suffer."},{"time":469756,"text":"Whether it's with this, whether it's with something else,"},{"time":471708,"text":"we all know what it is to hurt."},{"time":474535,"text":"We all know what it is to have pain in our heart,"},{"time":476373,"text":"and we all know how important it is to heal."},{"time":479067,"text":"But right now, depression is society's deep cut"},{"time":482461,"text":"that we're content to put a Band-Aid over and pretend it's not there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":485022,"text":"Well, it is there. It is there, and you know what? It's okay."},{"time":489526,"text":"Depression is okay. If you're going through it, know that you're okay."},{"time":493337,"text":"And know that you're sick, you're not weak,"},{"time":495999,"text":"and it's an issue, not an identity,"},{"time":497935,"text":"because when you get past the fear and the ridicule"},{"time":500688,"text":"and the judgment and the stigma of others,"},{"time":502485,"text":"you can see depression for what it really is,"},{"time":505471,"text":"and that's just a part of life,"},{"time":507710,"text":"just a part of life, and as much as I hate,"},{"time":511438,"text":"as much as I hate some of the places,"},{"time":513917,"text":"some of the parts of my life depression has dragged me down to,"},{"time":517013,"text":"in a lot of ways I'm grateful for it."},{"time":519548,"text":"Because yeah, it's put me in the valleys,"},{"time":521360,"text":"but only to show me there's peaks,"},{"time":522792,"text":"and yeah it's dragged me through the dark"},{"time":524391,"text":"but only to remind me there is light."},{"time":526977,"text":"My pain, more than anything in 19 years on this planet,"},{"time":530720,"text":"has given me perspective, and my hurt,"},{"time":532979,"text":"my hurt has forced me to have hope,"},{"time":535474,"text":"have hope and to have faith, faith in myself,"},{"time":538005,"text":"faith in others, faith that it can get better,"},{"time":540550,"text":"that we can change this, that we can speak up"},{"time":542628,"text":"and speak out and fight back against ignorance,"},{"time":545386,"text":"fight back against intolerance,"},{"time":547975,"text":"and more than anything,"},{"time":549990,"text":"learn to love ourselves,"},{"time":552716,"text":"learn to accept ourselves for who we are,"},{"time":554895,"text":"the people we are, not the people the world wants us to be."},{"time":558990,"text":"Because the world I believe in is one"},{"time":560602,"text":"where embracing your light doesn't mean ignoring your dark."},{"time":564770,"text":"The world I believe in is one where we're measured"},{"time":566851,"text":"by our ability to overcome adversities, not avoid them."},{"time":571367,"text":"The world I believe in is one where I can look someone in the eye"},{"time":575591,"text":"and say, \"I'm going through hell,\""},{"time":577353,"text":"and they can look back at me and go, \"Me too,\" and that's okay,"},{"time":580930,"text":"and it's okay because depression is okay. We're people."},{"time":584632,"text":"We're people, and we struggle and we suffer"},{"time":587062,"text":"and we bleed and we cry, and if you think that true strength"},{"time":589790,"text":"means never showing any weakness, then I'm here"},{"time":591909,"text":"to tell you you're wrong."},{"time":595155,"text":"You're wrong, because it's the opposite."},{"time":599052,"text":"We're people, and we have problems."},{"time":601736,"text":"We're not perfect, and that's okay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603407,"text":"So we need to stop the ignorance,"},{"time":605621,"text":"stop the intolerance, stop the stigma,"},{"time":608699,"text":"and stop the silence, and we need to take away the taboos,"},{"time":613273,"text":"take a look at the truth, and start talking,"},{"time":617812,"text":"because the only way we're going to beat a problem"},{"time":622536,"text":"that people are battling alone"},{"time":625870,"text":"is by standing strong together,"},{"time":629633,"text":"by standing strong together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":633397,"text":"And I believe that we can."},{"time":636376,"text":"I believe that we can. Thank you guys so much."},{"time":638295,"text":"This is a dream come true. Thank you. (Applause)"},{"time":640702,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}